author: cutting
msg: Fix HADOOP-166.  RPCs can now pass subclasses of declared types as parameters.  Note this change is incompatible for any application that stores ObjectWritables in a file.  Nutch only stores ObjectWritable in temporary intermediate files, so this is not a problem for Nutch.
